.container.mx-auto.p-4
  %h1.text-lg.font-semibold Sudoku Puzzle

  %table.table-auto.border-collapse.border.border-gray-900
    - @data.each do |row|
      %tr
        - row.each do |cell|
          %td.border.border-gray-900.w-8.h-8.text-center= cell || ""

  %p.mx-0.mt-4.text-sm.text-gray-600
    (The grid above is currently empty; real numbers will be filled in once
    a generator is implemented.)